            { id:"a-in-2", title:"owl:sameAs — linking to external datasets",
              detail:":Aspirin owl:sameAs <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aspirin> . Your Aspirin node is now connected to DBpedia, Wikidata, and PubChem automatically. Any query about Aspirin can pull in external data — clinical trial results, molecular structure, pricing — without storing any of it yourself. This is linked open data in practice." },
